    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanical integrity is prioritized with documented subframe reinforcement and a recent valve adjustment. Riding on a refined suspension with upgraded bushings, this chassis remains taut and communicative. A well-maintained example of Bavarian engineering, optimized for the discerning pilot.",
