      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep luster, with only the minor, expected signs of road use that come with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every button and dial functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound, having undergone regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance at certified intervals. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet, comfortable ride. I have kept comprehensive records of its service history, including recent brake and tire inspections. This is an ideal choice for a buyer who values a vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of reliable service. Smoke-free, pet-free, and garage-kept.",
